  <brief_title>How Improvement in Control of Diabetes Influences the Production of a Hormone Produced in the Gut Which Improves the Release and Action of Insulin.</brief_title>
  <acronym>MSD-GLP1</acronym>
  <official_title>Influence of Improving Glycaemic Control on Glucagon-Like-Peptide-1 Response to an Oral Glucose Load. Comparison of Sulphonylurea With DPP-4 Inhibition.</official_title>
